  '    <tr><td><code>system.security.assert.failure</code></td><td>Production posture assertion failed at boot — the deploy went out with a weak posture.</td><td>Any → page. The boot already failed; this is the post-mortem trail.</td></tr>',
  '    <tr><td><code>dual.grant.consumed</code></td><td>Destructive op ran with two-person approval. Compliance trail.</td><td>Daily digest. <code>dual.grant.expired</code> spike → ticket (workflow stalling).</td></tr>',
  '    <tr><td><code>retention.sweep.failed</code></td><td>Retention rule errored mid-run — data is older than the declared TTL.</td><td>Any → ticket. Repeated failure on the same rule → page.</td></tr>',
